metadata.name: The Milky Way shining in the night sky of Aso
metadata.description:
I took this picture of the great nature of Aso, the pride of Kyushu.

I took this photo of Aso Nakadake from the top of Mount Kijima.
This is a rare photo of Aso Nakadake with snow still on the ground, fire reflection, and the Milky Way together.

I hope you can feel the grandeur of Japan's nature through this photo.

Photo data
Taken on February 11, 2022
Size: 6192 × 8256
